Shawn W. WHITE & Kysha Tama Mordica, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Jeffrey D. FISHMAN, Trustee FOR the FMC PROFIT SHARING PLAN, a Trust, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-3748 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. June 08, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The parties' joint stipulation for dismissal of appeal filed June 7, 2018, is treated as a notice of voluntary dismissal and is granted. This appeal is dismissed.
